short_description:
- Versatile for all ages people for professional office bag, travel daypack, college/school backpack.
- Safe laptop sleeve, easy-access middle compartment, purse/wallet pocket, mobile-phone pocket.
- Made of Nylon material. Water repellent and spill proof.
- Includes 1 compartment for laptop & you can keep 3-4 cloth for business travel in other compartment, with the thick soft padding for the protection.
- Unique shoulder strap design with massage mats. Breathable cushion tight fits the back & shoulder.
- Light Weight & Comfortable Ergonomic Design.
price: Current Price: Rs.1,700, Original Price: Rs.
